{{Lunisolar March}} '''March 11''' is the 11th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * (【[318]】 _月_日) – The governor of the southern Yangtze region, {{ill|Sima Mo|ja|司馬寞|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, ascended to the throne proclaiming himself 【元帝】, and the {{ill|Eastern Jin|ja|東晋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was established. * {{ill|Eireki|ja|永暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1160]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Following defeat in the {{ill|Heiji Rebellion|ja|平治の乱|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was exiled to {{ill|Izu Province|ja|伊豆|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1192]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In the outskirts of the Southern Song capital, the {{ill|Lugou Bridge|ja|盧溝橋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (also known as Marco Polo Bridge) was constructed. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – After the combined forces of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|信長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|家康|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} defeated him, {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} committed suicide, leading to the downfall of the {{ill|Takeda clan|ja|武田氏|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1608]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Having resigned as Commander-in-Chief, {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} relocated to {{ill|Sunpu Castle|ja|駿府城|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
