== Births == * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1800]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Saira|ja|徳川斉昭|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 9th head of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|水戸藩主|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and father of {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1860]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1834]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hashimoto Sanao|ja|橋本左内|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a samurai of the {{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1859]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Shinmu Tennō|ja|神武天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 76th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[585 BC]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shinmu Tennō|ja|神武天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the first {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[585 BC]] or another traditional date). * ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[618]] {{ill|April 11|ja|4月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yang Emperor|ja|煬帝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 2nd emperor of the {{ill|Sui Dynasty|ja|隋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[569]]). * {{ill|Ōan|ja|応安|1=Ōan|lt=Ōan era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 23rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1368]] {{ill|March 29|ja|3月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Go-Murakami Tennō|ja|後村上天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 97th emperor (born [[1328]]). * In Tenshō 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a samurai and son of {{ill|Takeda Shingen|ja|武田信玄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (born [[1546]]).
