'''March 11''' is the 11th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝}}.

== Events ==
* (【[318]】 _月_日) – The governor of the southern Yangtze region, {{ill|Sima Mo|ja|司馬寞}}, ascended to the throne proclaiming himself 【元帝】, and the {{ill|Eastern Jin|ja|東晋}} was established.
* {{ill|Eireki|ja|永暦}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1160]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日}}) – Following defeat in the {{ill|Heiji Rebellion|ja|平治の乱}}, {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝}} was exiled to {{ill|Izu Province|ja|伊豆}}.
* ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1192]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日}}) – In the outskirts of the Southern Song capital, the {{ill|Lugou Bridge|ja|盧溝橋}} (also known as Marco Polo Bridge) was constructed.
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日}}) – After the combined forces of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|信長}} and {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|家康}} defeated him, {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼}} committed suicide, leading to the downfall of the {{ill|Takeda clan|ja|武田氏}}.
* {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1608]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日}}) – Having resigned as Commander-in-Chief, {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康}} relocated to {{ill|Sunpu Castle|ja|駿府城}}.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1800]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Saira|ja|徳川斉昭}}, the 9th head of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|水戸藩主}} and father of {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜}} (died [[1860]]).
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} [[1834]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日}}) – {{ill|Hashimoto Sanao|ja|橋本左内}}, a samurai of the {{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩}} (died [[1859]]).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Shinmu Tennō|ja|神武天皇}} 76th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[585 BC]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日}}) – {{ill|Shinmu Tennō|ja|神武天皇}}, the first {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇}} (born [[585 BC]] or another traditional date).
* ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[618]] {{ill|April 11|ja|4月11日}}) – {{ill|Yang Emperor|ja|煬帝}}, the 2nd emperor of the {{ill|Sui Dynasty|ja|隋}} (born [[569]]).
* {{ill|Ōan|ja|応安|1=Ōan|lt=Ōan era}} 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平}} 23rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1368]] {{ill|March 29|ja|3月29日}}) – {{ill|Go-Murakami Tennō|ja|後村上天皇}}, the 97th emperor (born [[1328]]).
* In Tenshō 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日}}) – {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼}}, a samurai and son of {{ill|Takeda Shingen|ja|武田信玄}} (born [[1546]]).

