* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1834]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hashimoto Sanao|ja|橋本左内|qq=|12=draft}}, a samurai of the {{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|qq=|12=draft}} (died [[1859]]).

