* ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[618]] {{ill|April 11|ja|4月11日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yang Emperor|ja|煬帝|qq=|12=draft}}, the 2nd emperor of the {{ill|Sui Dynasty|ja|隋|qq=|12=draft}} (born [[569]]).
* {{ill|Ōan|ja|応安|1=Ōan|lt=Ōan era|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=|12=draft}} 23rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1368]] {{ill|March 29|ja|3月29日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Go-Murakami Tennō|ja|後村上天皇|qq=|12=draft}}, the 97th emperor (born [[1328]]).
