'''March 11''' is the 11th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* (【[318]】 _月_日) – The governor of the southern Yangtze region, {{ill|Sima Mo|ja|司馬寞|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, ascended to the throne proclaiming himself 【元帝】, and the {{ill|Eastern Jin|ja|東晋|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} was established.
* {{ill|Eireki|ja|永暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1160]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Following defeat in the {{ill|Heiji Rebellion|ja|平治の乱|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} was exiled to {{ill|Izu Province|ja|伊豆|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}.
* ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1192]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In the outskirts of the Southern Song capital, the {{ill|Lugou Bridge|ja|盧溝橋|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} (also known as Marco Polo Bridge) was constructed.
* {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – After the combined forces of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|信長|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|家康|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} defeated him, {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} committed suicide, leading to the downfall of the {{ill|Takeda clan|ja|武田氏|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1608]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Having resigned as Commander-in-Chief, {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} relocated to {{ill|Sunpu Castle|ja|駿府城|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1800]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Saira|ja|徳川斉昭|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 9th head of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|水戸藩主|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} and father of {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1860]]).
* {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1834]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hashimoto Sanao|ja|橋本左内|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}}, a samurai of the {{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|qq=|12=draft|12=draft}} (died [[1859]]).

