== Events == * (【[318]】 _月_日) – The governor of the southern Yangtze region, {{ill|Sima Mo|ja|司馬寞|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sima Mo|qq=}}, ascended to the throne proclaiming himself 【元帝】, and the {{ill|Eastern Jin|ja|東晋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eastern Jin|qq=}} was established. * {{ill|Eireki|ja|永暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eireki|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1160]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 19|qq=}}) – Following defeat in the {{ill|Heiji Rebellion|ja|平治の乱|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heiji Rebellion|qq=}}, {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoritomo|qq=}} was exiled to {{ill|Izu Province|ja|伊豆|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izu Province|qq=}}. * ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1192]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 24|qq=}}) – In the outskirts of the Southern Song capital, the {{ill|Lugou Bridge|ja|盧溝橋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lugou Bridge|qq=}} (also known as Marco Polo Bridge) was constructed. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 3|qq=}}) – After the combined forces of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|信長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobunaga|qq=}} and {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|家康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} defeated him, {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Katsuyori|qq=}} committed suicide, leading to the downfall of the {{ill|Takeda clan|ja|武田氏|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda clan|qq=}}. * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1608]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 25|qq=}}) – Having resigned as Commander-in-Chief, {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} relocated to {{ill|Sunpu Castle|ja|駿府城|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sunpu Castle|qq=}}.
== Births == * {{ill|Kansei|ja|寛政|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kansei|qq=}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1800]] {{ill|April 4|ja|4月4日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 4|qq=}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Saira|ja|徳川斉昭|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Saira|qq=}}, the 9th head of the {{ill|Mito Domain|ja|水戸藩主|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mito Domain|qq=}} and father of {{ill|Tokugawa Yoshinobu|ja|徳川慶喜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Yoshinobu|qq=}} (died [[1860]]). * {{ill|Tenpō|ja|天保|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpō|qq=}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1834]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 19|qq=}}) – {{ill|Hashimoto Sanao|ja|橋本左内|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hashimoto Sanao|qq=}}, a samurai of the {{ill|Fukui Domain|ja|福井藩|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fukui Domain|qq=}} (died [[1859]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Shinmu Tennō|ja|神武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinmu Tennō|qq=}} 76th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[585 BC]] {{ill|April 9|ja|4月9日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 9|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shinmu Tennō|ja|神武天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shinmu Tennō|qq=}}, the first {{ill|Emperor of Japan|ja|天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor of Japan|qq=}} (born [[585 BC]] or another traditional date). * ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[618]] {{ill|April 11|ja|4月11日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 11|qq=}}) – {{ill|Yang Emperor|ja|煬帝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Emperor|qq=}}, the 2nd emperor of the {{ill|Sui Dynasty|ja|隋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sui Dynasty|qq=}} (born [[569]]). * {{ill|Ōan|ja|応安|1=Ōan|lt=Ōan era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōan|13=User:Immanuelle/Ōan|qq=}} 1st year/{{ill|Shōhei|ja|正平|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shōhei|qq=}} 23rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1368]] {{ill|March 29|ja|3月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 29|qq=}}) – {{ill|Go-Murakami Tennō|ja|後村上天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Go-Murakami Tennō|qq=}}, the 97th emperor (born [[1328]]). * In Tenshō 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 3|qq=}}) – {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Katsuyori|qq=}}, a samurai and son of {{ill|Takeda Shingen|ja|武田信玄|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Shingen|qq=}} (born [[1546]]).
