ma period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 3|qq=}}) – After the combined forces of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|信長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobunaga|qq=}} and {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|家康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} defeated him, {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Katsuyori|qq=}} committed suicide, leading to the downfall of the {{ill|Takeda clan|ja|武田氏|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda clan|qq=}}. * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1608]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 25|qq=}}) – Having resigned as Commander-in-Chief, {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} relocated to {{ill|Sunpu Castle|ja|駿府城|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sunpu Castle|qq=}}.
