{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=三月十一|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 3월 11일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar March|qq=}} '''March 11''' is the 11th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Senshō|ja|先勝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senshō|qq=}}.
== Events == * (【[318]】 _月_日) – The governor of the southern Yangtze region, {{ill|Sima Mo|ja|司馬寞|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sima Mo|qq=}}, ascended to the throne proclaiming himself 【元帝】, and the {{ill|Eastern Jin|ja|東晋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eastern Jin|qq=}} was established. * {{ill|Eireki|ja|永暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Eireki|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1160]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 19|qq=}}) – Following defeat in the {{ill|Heiji Rebellion|ja|平治の乱|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heiji Rebellion|qq=}}, {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoritomo|qq=}} was exiled to {{ill|Izu Province|ja|伊豆|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Izu Province|qq=}}. * ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1192]] {{ill|April 24|ja|4月24日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 24|qq=}}) – In the outskirts of the Southern Song capital, the {{ill|Lugou Bridge|ja|盧溝橋|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lugou Bridge|qq=}} (also known as Marco Polo Bridge) was constructed. * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 3|qq=}}) – After the combined forces of {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|信長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oda Nobunaga|qq=}} and {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|家康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} defeated him, {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Katsuyori|qq=}} committed suicide, leading to the downfall of the {{ill|Takeda clan|ja|武田氏|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda clan|qq=}}. * {{ill|Keichō|1=Keichō|2=ja|3=慶長|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Keichō|qq=}} 13rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} [[1608]] {{ill|April 25|ja|4月25日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 25|qq=}}) – Having resigned as Commander-in-Chief, {{ill|Tokugawa Ieyasu|ja|徳川家康|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tokugawa Ieyasu|qq=}} relocated to {{ill|Sunpu Castle|ja|駿府城|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sunpu Castle|qq=}}.
