リウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1368]] {{ill|March 29|ja|3月29日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March 29|qq=}}) – {{ill|Go-Murakami Tennō|ja|後村上天皇|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Go-Murakami Tennō|qq=}}, the 97th emperor (born [[1328]]). * In Tenshō 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1582]] {{ill|April 3|ja|4月3日|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/April 3|qq=}}) – {{ill|Takeda Katsuyori|ja|武田勝頼|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Katsuyori|qq=}}, a samurai and son of {{ill|Takeda Shingen|ja|武田信玄|qq=|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeda Shingen|qq=}} (born [[1546]]).
