== Deaths == * [[:en:Emperor Jimmu|Shinmu Tennō]] 76th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[585 BC]] [[:en:April 9|April 9]]) – [[:en:Emperor Jimmu|Shinmu Tennō]], the first [[:en:Emperor of Japan|Emperor of Japan]] (born [[585 BC]] or another traditional date). * ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[618]] [[:en:April 11|April 11]]) – [[:en:Emperor Yang of Sui|Yang Emperor]], the 2nd emperor of the [[:en:Sui dynasty|Sui Dynasty]] (born [[569]]). * [[:en:Ōan|Ōan era]] 1st year/[[:en:Zhengping|Shōhei]] 23rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1368]] [[:en:March 29|March 29]]) – [[:en:Emperor Go-Murakami|Go-Murakami Tennō]], the 97th emperor (born [[1328]]). * In Tenshō 10th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[1582]] [[:en:April 3|April 3]]) – [[:en:Takeda Katsuyori|Takeda Katsuyori]], a samurai and son of [[:en:Takeda Shingen|Takeda Shingen]] (born [[1546]]).
